325389 THE CONSTITUTION (SCHEDULED CASTES) ORDER (AMENDMENT) ACT, 2002
ACT NO. 25 OF 2002 [ 24th May, 2002.]
An Act further to amend the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) Order, 1950.
BE it enacted by Parliament in the Fifty- third Year of the Republic of India as follows:-
1360284 1Short title.- This Act may be called the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) Order (Amendment) Act, 2002.
1652008 2 Amendment of the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) Order, 1950.- The Schedule to the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) Order, 1950 is hereby amended in the manner and to the extent specified hereunder, namely:-
